            <article class="post-77375 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-77375">
  <header class="entry-header">

          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2019/12/tuesday-assorted-non-links-and-links.html">Tuesday assorted non-links and links</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
        <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2019-12-31 11:54:09">December 31, 2019 at 11:54 am </time>
                                          </div><!-- /.byline -->
  </header><!-- /.entry-header -->
  <div class="entry-content">
    <div class="pf-content"><p>1. Cocoman&#8217;s Law?: &#8220;The more important is an investigation of applied synthetic knowledge, the less useful literature there will be.&#8221;</p>
<p>2. <a href="https://radicalxchange.org/blog/posts/2019-12-30-gqx4th/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">E. Glen Weyl summary of RadicalxChange as an intellectual and political program</a>.</p>
<p>3. <a href="https://gizmodo.com/how-to-hypothetically-hack-your-schools-surveillance-1840680142" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">How to hypothetically hack your school&#8217;s surveillance of you</a>.</p>
<p>4. <a href="https://medium.com/@anna.zaitsev/response-to-critique-on-our-paper-algorithmic-extremism-examining-youtubes-rabbit-hole-of-8b53611ce903" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ledwich and Zaitsev respond on YouTube radicalization</a>.</p>
<p>5. <a href="http://www.rfi.fr/en/france/20191228-board-game-french-wealth-gap-unexpected-christmas-hit-kapital-strikes-pension-macron?ref=em" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">New French board game on wealth gap is a big hit</a>.</p>
<p>6. <a href="https://www.edworkingpapers.com/ai20-188" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The value of air filters in classrooms, to limit air pollution</a>.</p>
<p>7. <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/2019/12/gertrude-himmelfarb-historian-moral-change/604276/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=share" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gertrude Himmelfarb has passed away</a>.</p>
</div>
  </div><!-- /.entry-content -->
  <footer class="entry-footer">

