          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2019/12/sunday-assorted-links-244.html">Sunday assorted links</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
