<p>4. <a href="https://khn.org/news/hospital-group-mum-as-members-pursue-patients-with-lawsuits-and-debt-collectors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mostly non-profit hospitals</a>: &#8220;Atlantic Health System, whose CEO is the AHA’s chairman, Brian Gragnolati, has sued patients for unpaid bills thousands of times this year, court records show, including a family struggling to pay bills for three children with cystic fibrosis.&#8221;</p>
<p>5. <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/books/2019/dec/29/alasdair-gray-influential-scottish-writer-and-artist-dies-aged-85" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alasdair Gray of Lanark fame has passed away</a>.</p>
